body_html:
@tensorflowbutler
Have i written custom code: No, i haven't. I just started learning to code 3 days ago and found understanding tensorflow could be a powerful tool for different engineer mechanisms.
OS platform and distribution: macOS High Sierra 10.13.1 64 bit
TensorFlow installed from: https://www.tensorflow.org/versions/master/install/install_mac
TensorFlow Version: Latest. I used Python 2.7 and pip was already upgraded.
Bazel version: ...
CUDE/cuDNN version:
GPU model, memory: Intel HD Graphics 4000 1536 MB, 8GB 1600 MHz DDR3
Exact command to reproduce: $ pip install tensorflow

Problem: I already tried to install through native pip and Virtuaenv. In both, i get the same error where to error starts at line 215 in the "main" function from the pip/basecommand.py file.
